<p>A dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تنظيف-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=524" > cleaning teeth </a> indicates improved circumstances and livelihood, and other interpretations. We will translate it for a single woman, married woman, pregnant woman, divorced woman, or man, such as teeth brushing at the dentist, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تنظيف-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=524" > cleaning teeth </a> by hand, or with floss, according to Ibn Sirin, Imam al-Sadiq, and others at the bottom:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تفريش-الأسنان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=29" > brushing teeth </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Brushing teeth in dreams indicates an improvement in relationships between family and relatives, good circumstances, and improvement in life, because the mouth is the source that shows a person's affairs, so anything the dreamer sees about a change in the mouth indicates a change in the situation, so if the change is good, such as cleaning the mouth or teeth, this indicates that happy developments and changes will occur in the dreamer's life, even if the change is bad, such as tooth loss or <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-خروج-الدم-من-الفم-في-المنام?page=952" > blood coming out of the mouth </a>. Unhappy changes in the dreamer's life.</p>
<p>And if you saw that you went to the dentist in a dream to take care of your teeth, then this means that you will have the opportunity to prove your loyalty, work, and respect to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a> and deal with him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
