<p><span></span></p>
<p>But if you see him cleaning the girl's teeth, then this means that calamities and scandals will happen to someone close to you.</p>
<p>When a person, whether male or female, sees that he is brushing his teeth, if he used an ordinary brush and cleaned it properly, this indicates a good relationship with those around him from relatives, especially his family, parents, and brothers, and in addition to that, the wife and children for the married and the children, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تنظيف-الأسنان-في-المنام?page=524" > cleaning teeth </a> from a distance indicates friends and acquaintances.</p>
<p>As for purifying it with a miswak, it is good, for some say: good following of the Sunnah and religion, and some interpret it as livelihood and happiness in this world, and others say that it is a cure for diseases or an escape from sorrow and grief. And the cessation of grief for a man, woman, or girl.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
