</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In the case of using other things in purification, such as a stick, rope, spoon, or the like, if the purity is correct, it takes the meaning of good, and if it is in a wrong way, then the ruler must think about the path he chooses and correct the path of his life.<br/>And if his teeth loosen during cleaning, this is an attempt by people to cause him trouble.  Salvation from their deception and planning. These problems can be at work, with family, or married life and partnership.</p>
<p>As for anyone who sees blood flowing from his teeth with a brush, this is a removal of sins and worries from life and happiness that enters and rejoices, and if he is not a sincere seeker of his religion, he is the one who slanders. People and eat their flesh with forbidden words in their presentation and state.</p>
<p>And whoever sees, whether male or female, that his teeth are becoming more contaminated, this increases the worries of his life, or an indication of illness.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
