<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تفريش-الأسنان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=29" > brushing teeth </a> in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>Dream interpreter Muhammad ibn Sirin said that seeing yourself brushing your teeth in a dream means that the dreamer has a lot of self-confidence, strength, and energy, and that brushing your teeth in a dream means that you are trying to express important feelings to others.  Or the behavior of the people around you.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
