</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>Brushing your teeth in your dream indicates an increase in your luck in matters of love and relationships, and if you love someone, then this dream may be a sign that the time has come to get closer to that other person and express your feelings to him.  This dream also means that you may be healthy, and if you are sick, this dream means that you will be able to recover and feel better quickly.</p>
<p><span></span><span></span></p>
<p>If you dream that you are brushing your teeth with a toothbrush, it means that you need to take care of yourself, and this can be an indication that you are not taking care of yourself properly.<br/>Brushing your teeth in a dream may indicate that you are worried about some unexpected problems that have happened to you.</p>
