<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تفريش-الأسنان-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=29" > brushing teeth </a> at the dentist in a dream</span></h2>
<p>If a person sees that he is cleaning them with a doctor or dentist and working on repairing or cleaning them, then he suspects himself towards others who are in his place, and if this doctor heals him or purifies him completely, he is the winner and the winner.  over those who try to deceive him.<br/>And if the doctor deceives him and works to deceive the person, then this is a calamity on his family, and he is blamed for it and turns against him.  And if the girl sees that she is undergoing treatment with a male doctor, then this is a scandal in a matter that she is concealing, and her treatment with a female doctor is a gain for her in her mother's love.<br/>And <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الرجل-في-المنام?page=447" > seeing a man </a> that he is with a female doctor, this is his attempt to follow forbidden things on him, and the presence of the man with a male doctor is an increase in his relationship with his family, as long as the doctor does not deceive any of the above, does not increase his suffering, and does not contaminate his teeth.</p>
<p>And whoever sees that he is a doctor, if he treats a man in this way, this is good knowledge and a good relationship between them, but if he treats the teeth of a girl or a girl he knows from his relatives, such as his sister, daughter, niece, or nephew, then he solves a thorny problem for her or an accusation against her, and if he treats one of his relatives, such as his mother, aunt, or uncle.  Or a grandmother or wife, he benefits from her or helps her to benefit from her and helps her in her life.</p>
<p>But if he cleans the teeth of an unknown person who knows her and is not from her Mahrams, then this is a scandal that she heard about, and if she does not know her, then it is harm that falls on her through women's conspiracies.</p>
