<h3><strong>Dream interpretation of riding with one person</strong></h3>
<p>If a single woman dreams that she is riding a horse with <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شخص-غريب-في-المنام?page=754" > a stranger </a>, this is a sign that someone is approaching her engagement, and although she will not know him beforehand, she will love him very much, because she will find with him the security and safety that she is looking for in her life.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
